## Fastpath Host Setup Test

1. Run `./scripts/configure_fastpath_host.sh --host <FASTPATH_HOST>` from the repo root.
2. SSH into the host (`ssh ubuntu@<FASTPATH_HOST>`) and verify `~/.bashrc` or `~/.profile` contains `export PATH=$HOME/venv/bin:$HOME/fastpath/fastpath:$PATH`.
3. Start a fresh SSH session and execute `fastpath --help`; expect the usage banner (no ModuleNotFound errors).
4. Optionally run `which fastpath` to ensure it resolves to `~/fastpath/fastpath/fastpath` and `python3 --version` shows the venv interpreter (`~/venv/bin/python3`).

Replace `<FASTPATH_HOST>` with the target IP/hostname (e.g., 54.172.102.176).
